Request comes in
  → helmet checks headers (security)
  → passport-jwt extracts token (auth)
  → class-validator validates body (validation)
  → your controller runs
  → prisma queries PostgreSQL (database)
  → bull queues background work (jobs)
    → sendgrid sends email (async)
    → openai generates AI content (async)
  → socket.io pushes real-time updates (websockets)
  → stripe handles payment (payments)
  → response sent back
